{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerechte Regeln f\u00fcr Globalisierung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.600", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daf\u00fcr wollen wir mit unserem Antrag einen Beitrag leisten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.360", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Deutschland wissen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.760", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wichtig es ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.280", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schutz f\u00fcr Investitionen und Schutz f\u00fcr Eigentum zu leisten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit die Wirtschaftsentwicklung und damit die Wohlfahrt der Menschen gew\u00e4hrleistet ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.760", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch weltweit gilt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.560", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die L\u00e4nder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.680", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen Eigentum gesichert ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.160", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind wirtschaftlich erfolgreicher und k\u00f6nnen ihren Einwohnern bessere Lebensbedingungen bieten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.640", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Internationale Direktinvestitionen leisten einen bedeutenden Beitrag zur \u00dcberwindung von Hunger und Armut und zur Wohlfahrtssteigerung in allen beteiligten L\u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist internationaler Investitionsschutz ein wichtiges Ziel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.920", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das bislang alle Bundesregierungen unterst\u00fctzt haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.400", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So hat zum Beispiel die rot-gr\u00fcne Regierung von 1998 bis 2005\u00a0 23\u00a0bilaterale Investitionsschutzabkommen unterzeichnet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.920", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Schiedsgerichtsklauseln enthalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.320", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das erkennen wir an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Zahl internationaler Schiedsverfahren hat sich in den letzten Jahrzehnten leicht erh\u00f6ht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.680", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist bei knapp 3\u00a0000 neu abgeschlossenen Investitionsvertr\u00e4gen und stark steigenden Direktinvestitionen auch nicht anders zu erwarten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2017 gab es weltweit 65\u00a0neue Investor-Staat-Schiedsgerichtsverfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.800", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das zeigt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.600", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Unternehmen wenden diese Mittel nur restriktiv an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen aber auch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Je verflochtener die Weltwirtschaft wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "umso besser und pr\u00e4ziser m\u00fcssen auch unsere Abkommen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.880", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und wir brauchen transparentere Verfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die M\u00f6glichkeit von Revisionsentscheidungen und unabh\u00e4ngigen Schiedsgerichten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.480", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Ziel ist die Installation eines multinationalen Investitionsgerichtes. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern die Bundesregierung auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.680", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich auf EU-Ebene international intensiv daf\u00fcr einzusetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.280", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das zu erreichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist wahrscheinlich eine Generationenaufgabe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.160", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber die Frage ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was tun wir in der Zwischenzeit? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.240", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen wir einfach keinen internationalen Investitionsschutz mehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.440", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu dem Preis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.760", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Direktinvestitionen unterbleiben und damit Menschen die Chance auf Entwicklung und Wohlstand verlieren? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oder wollen wir nicht doch lieber ein bislang bew\u00e4hrtes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.000", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "funktionierendes System erhalten und verbessern?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.680", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir schlagen in unserem Antrag vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.520", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das System der Investitionsschutzabkommen zu verbessern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein entscheidendes Problem besteht in der Vereinbarkeit von Schiedsgerichtsklauseln mit dem EU-Recht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.080", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Urteil des EuGH im M\u00e4rz stellt faktisch alle Schiedsgerichtsklauseln in internationalen Vertr\u00e4gen erst einmal unter Vorbehalt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.640", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Sie klatschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber damit entsteht eine riesige Rechtsunsicherheit f\u00fcr Unternehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.800", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Vertrauen auf v\u00f6lkerrechtlich g\u00fcltige Vertr\u00e4ge investiert haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.280", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen Unternehmen schulden wir Vertrauensschutz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.000", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung glaubt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.000", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Urteil w\u00fcrde Vertr\u00e4ge mit Drittstaaten nicht betreffen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.120", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber Meinen und Glauben bringen leider keine Rechtssicherheit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.040", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung muss jetzt auf EU-Ebene politische Initiativen ergreifen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit rechtssicher klar ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche Vertr\u00e4ge zweifelsfrei weiter gelten und wo es problematisch wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.920", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese m\u00fcssen dann in einem geordneten Verfahren in EU-kompatible Strukturen \u00fcberf\u00fchrt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Unterst\u00fctzung haben Sie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb sollten Sie auch unseren Antrag unterst\u00fctzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.720", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.920", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Weeser.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner in der Debatte: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.960", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stefan Rouenhoff f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}